      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S OUR GAL (7) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at Capalaba in a handy 19.89 beating Jet Springer. Expected to go well again. DAYSEA'S KURT (6) will take beating coming off a quick 19.61 victory at this track over 352m. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. SHIMMERING REIGN (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (30.74) in a Mix 5 at Q Parklands. Has a good record at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from seven attempts. Shapes as one to consider. INFRA TERRA (3) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
